lead_paragraph: Bangladesh is hopeful England will go ahead with their planned tour of the South Asian country later this year despite Friday's attack by gunmen at an upmarket Dhaka restaurant that left 20 dead.

headline.print_headline: Bangladesh Hopeful of England Visit Despite Dhaka Attack
